Prerequistes to build:
======================

    - a C++ compiler (tested on gcc 3.3 and up)
    - libboost (boost::shared_ptr)
    - libjpeg

    - automake/autoconf
  or
    - CMake 2.4 <http://cmake.org>


Supported file format:
======================

    - Canon CR2
    - Canon CRW
    - Nikon NEF
    - Olympus ORF: E-300
    - Pentax PEF
    - DNG
    - Sony ARW


How to build:
=============

  Using automake/autoconf:

    $ mkdir libopenraw-ambuild && cd libopenraw-ambuild
    $ autoreconf --install --symlink ../libopenraw
    $ ../libopenraw/configure --prefix=...
    $ make
    $ make install DESTDIR=...

  Using cmake:

    $ mkdir libopenraw-build && cd libopenraw-build
    $ cmake ../libopenraw
    $ make
    $ make install DESTDIR=...


Support table:
==============

  T  Tested and proven to work. (I have a sample.)
  Y  Yes, it is there. (Untested as I do not have a sample but the format
     is known to be similar.)
  N  Not supported.
  B  Known to be Broken. (Needs to be fixed. I have a sample but further
     work is required.)


